          },
          "reviewBody": "A very nice school for kids as well as for grown ups, the teaching staff is very corporative and efficient towards their work. This school has the best environment which any other school could have. Not only academics but they also look forward towards sport and encourage Children to participate in extra curricular activity. Best for my child and could for yours too..",
          "publisher": {
