            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "One of the key strengths of Greater Valley School is its commitment to providing a holistic education that focuses on the overall development of each student. The school offers a range of extracurricular activities, including sports, music, dance, drama, and art, to help students develop their talents and interests. There are also various clubs and societies that allow students to explore their interests and pursue their passions.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
